column1: Table 4.  Justice system expenditure by character, state and type of government, fiscal year 2007
Series title:  Justice Expenditure and Employment Extracts 2007, NCJ 231540
Data source:  Criminal Justice Expenditure and Employment Extracts Program (CJEE)
Table 4.   Justice system expenditure by character, state and type of government, fiscal year 2007
Notes:  Local government data are estimates subject to variability.

a/ For each state and the United States summary, the expenditure figures shown on the "local, total" lines and the combined state-local total lines (opposite each state's name) exclude duplicative intergovernmental transactions.  Thus, the "local, total" lines include intergovernmental payments only to the state government and the combined state-local total lines exclude all intergovernmental payments.
